VALENTINE’S DAY and the Men’s
Conference are around the corner and if awujoli you are in trouble.  The #UmjoloWouldBeFunIf has
been trending on Twitter, and tweeps say if somethings were not included in umjolo –
things would be simpler.  Martin Hlawu said umjolo
would be nice if: “this other gender would understand that Valentine’s day is
for lovers, to appreciate the person you love not someone’s birthday.”                  